params_used.custom_text:
// This module categorizes WiFi signal strength based on the received signal in dBm.
// It outputs a 3-bit value where:
// 000 indicates very strong signal (> -50 dBm)
// 001 indicates strong signal (-50 to -60 dBm)
// 010 indicates moderate signal (-60 to -70 dBm)
// 011 indicates weak signal (-70 to -80 dBm)
// 100 indicates very weak signal (< -80 dBm)
